today.
</P>
<P>
The total market volume increased to 301.84 million units,
valued at 650.3 million Singapore dollars (about 445.41 million US
dollars). Advances overwhelmed declines by 289 to 79, while 249
other counters remained unchanged.
</P>
<P>
Tianjin Zhong Xin was the most actively traded stock as it
registered a turnover of 14.97 million units. It was followed by
Aztech System which had 14.44 million shares traded. Westmont Land
was next with 12.61 million of its shares changed hands.
</P>
