it declined by 60 cents to end at 25 Singapore dollars. City
Developments warrant fell by 40 cents to close at 10.9 Singapore
dollars, while City Developments finished 30 cents lower at 13.7
Singapore dollars. The Overseas Union Bank (OUB) Foreign and the
Thai Prime Fund also dropped by 30 cents each to close at 9.55
Singapore dollars and 9.3 US dollars respectively.  
