<HEADLINE> Malawi President Drops Charges Against </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
LUSAKA, July 24 (Xinhua) -- Malawi President Bakili Muluzi has
asked Director of Public Prosecutions Kamudoni Nyasulu to
consider dropping all criminal charges against former president
Hastings Kamuzu Banda.
</P>
<P>
