JAKARTA, July 24 (Xinhua) -- Indonesian President Suharto held
talks last night with visiting Cambodian First Prime Minister
Prince Norodom Ranariddh who was ousted two weeks ago by his rival
Second Prime Minister Hun Sen, an Indonesian foreign ministry
official said today.
</P>
