<HEADLINE> Hingis Powers Past Maleeva </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
WASHINGTON, July 23 (Xinhua) -- Top seed Martina Hingis had six
aces for an easy 6-1, 6-2 victory over Magdalena Maleeva in her
second round Wednesday night in the 450,000 U.S. dollars Bank of
the West women's tournament in California.
</P>
<P>
Hingis, who kept a 47-1 record this year, sealed up the
competition in 50 minutes.
</P>
