ceremony at a school in Tricomalee on July 6 and Maharoof was shot
dead together with five others when his jeep was ambushed by the
rebels last Sunday.
</P>
<P>
The sources said the LTTE rebels are targeting all those
opposed to their separate state for which they have been waging a
14-year war.
</P>
<P>
The MPs in the East are no longer able to live in their home
with their families due to security threat, the sources quoted the
Speaker as saying. 
