<HEADLINE> China Not To Sacrifice Environment for Economic Growth: Premier (2) </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
He stressed that all the major industrial polluters in the
country must meet national standards when draining off their foul
air and water by the end of this year, and drinking water for
