along with Athens, Cape Town, Rome and Stockhold from among 11
candidates.
</P>
<P>
The International Olympic Committee (IOC) will cast its final
votes on September 5 for the eventual host.
</P>
<P>
Rio de Janeiro, as well as Istanbul, Lille, San Juan, Seville
and St Petersburg were dropped from the list. 
